Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.88,0:00:23.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.44,0:00:29.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光 至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.62,0:00:43.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然  充滿疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.74,0:00:51.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友一起度過每一天 直到將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.96,0:00:58.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流著眼淚  無法釋懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.71,0:01:09.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想請教  如何追回失去的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.81,0:01:16.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.52,0:01:22.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.11,0:01:28.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.25,0:01:33.09,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把謎團解開吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.53,0:21:34.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我們兩人會相遇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.92,0:21:43.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起共看如此淒涼的夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.88,0:21:50.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索枯陽找尋能吸引他的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.38,0:21:59.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻找不出分離仍能相聚的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.02,0:22:08.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色雖然有時難看只要能以笑臉拂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.36,0:22:16.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爭執偶而有之但是也能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.62,0:22:26.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要唯一的願望可以實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.71,0:22:35.01,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.42,0:00:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 閃耀的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心疲累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.59,0:00:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一帖良藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的地點繼續在山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.13,0:00:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清新的空氣將事件撥雲見日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.16,0:00:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.66,0:00:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.57,0:00:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.86,0:01:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.73,0:01:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完成了一件不露痕跡的行動以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.72,0:01:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX這個著名的職業殺手就從此消失了蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這個FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然接下一個取委託人性命的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.58,0:01:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那個人就是不動產公司的社長潮文造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔接受了他的委託而擔任他的保鑣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.65,0:01:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小蘭也來到一片翠綠的丹原山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行登山活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.27,0:02:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們之外還有五個登山客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私人公司職員的高梨亘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學登山社社員平井健一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.40,0:02:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小說家自居的能勢新吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常做徒步旅行的三枝恭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.52,0:02:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她的男朋友河邊晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.88,0:02:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這五個人裡很有可能有一個就是FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.23,0:02:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮先生當初對FOX提出殺他的條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.22,0:02:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要在他進行登山活動的時候下手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一件命案很快就發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在懷疑到底是誰殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.08,0:02:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又發生了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.84,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖登山殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 我馬上就來了 妳等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.09,0:03:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.81,0:03:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.09,0:03:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳...沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在擔心妳被殺了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是有人被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是恭子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.87,0:03:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼會被殺呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是用刀子做的案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是FOX做的第二件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭…恭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰殺死了恭子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.57,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把刀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由左邊斜斜的插下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是慣用左手的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 兇手到底為什麼非殺她不可呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.77,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才這個姐姐是自己一個人在休息站的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛才不就是在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天一亮的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家就分頭出去找爸爸你們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候大家都在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每個人都往不同的方向去找你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們根本不知道你們去了哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.08,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們都沒有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用左手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得能勢先生應該是慣用右手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰為了什麼目的殺人的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把一切對大家說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上在我們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個叫做FOX的職業殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是這一連續殺人事件的罪魁禍首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說那個職業殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探先生 這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有兩個人連續被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情不能再瞞下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 不能再有人被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.82,0:04:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在還沒有證據說這兩件案子是一個人所做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 偵探先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.91,0:05:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個FOX的真正身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.24,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名偵探毛利小五郎早就已經知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.52,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？ 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探毛利小五郎先生果然厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鬧得滿城風雨的職業殺手FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX平常慣用左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從屍體身上的刀子角度來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個殺害三枝恭子小姐的人也是以左手行兇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.18,0:05:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之中就有一個人是慣用左手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我們之中唯一一個慣用左手的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.41,0:05:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是昨天才剛剛落崖身亡的平井先生吧？ 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.46,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼看來你這個人的確是觀察的非常入微 能勢先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過怎麼說我也是個小說家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.29,0:05:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏銳的觀察和好奇心是我吃飯的本錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一樣 你刻意隱藏的那隻慣用的左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.88,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也是你寫小說這一行重要的本錢之一吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.23,0:05:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎麼掩飾也沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恐怕原本慣用的是左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是後來刻意改成右手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你左右手都能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且用起來都很順手吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.98,0:06:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能勢先生慣用兩隻手的確沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.39,0:06:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是這件命案的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時是個把刀射出去殺人的FOX的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說家能勢新吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.56,0:06:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫我太吃驚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我大名鼎鼎的職業殺手FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看你別做偵探改寫小說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少給我裝蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小說裡面也寫過職業殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就是以你實際的經驗寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.66,0:06:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這個傢伙真的就是那個FOX嗎？偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼 我呼吸不過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮先生 請你稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能使用暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要對這傢伙討回一筆債
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.58,0:07:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.91,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.99,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮先生失去理智 可能會殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.01,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.18,0:07:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛線絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.97,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顏色是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.04,0:07:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.92,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.24,0:07:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人真的是那個叫FOX的職業殺手殺的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個節骨眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少在那兒說些廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用不分青紅皂白的就亂罵人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼那麼說呢 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直認為兇手只有可能是從她後面用左手攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.74,0:07:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.51,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個兇手也很有可能是從這個姐姐的正面把刀刺下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.43,0:07:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的意思就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你現在扮演她一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這把刀繞到後面刺下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話兇手就會是用右手犯案的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.75,0:07:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果要做這種動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不可能是偷偷摸摸的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.67,0:08:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.60,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對被害人而言不會讓她感覺見外的人就是兇手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的指甲裡面還夾了幾根毛線頭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.81,0:08:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個顏色是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一一個穿著這種顏色毛衣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能夠在她不懷疑之下行兇的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.84,0:08:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是河邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的意思是說他就是FOX嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這也太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX明明是慣用左手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河邊先生慣用的是右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件命案到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.15,0:08:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個包包裡面裝了好多一萬元的鈔票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還有血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.56,0:08:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個姐姐幾乎沒有流什麼血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這就是別人的血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個血跡還很新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會是誰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這個謎題好像越來越難解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.76,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下我又有東西可以寫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 潮先生到哪去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.14,0:09:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛明明還在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他剛才氣沖沖地跑出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會不會是跑出去追河邊先生了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮先生是FOX的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓他落單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個管理員好像也不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他是被河邊先生抓去當人質了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他對這附近的路很熟悉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個就暫時留在這裡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如果要管理員幫他認路的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定不會走原來上山的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 他一定會選擇比較危險的路走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想死吧 老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地…地震？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 來人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 那個石頭快要掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.36,0:10:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.99,0:10:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.00,0:10:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 爬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快 那個岩石要掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千鈞一髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.35,0:10:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.16,0:10:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮先生他們人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他兩個人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.06,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個管理員把我推了一把 他就跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他回到休息站去就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條山路已經被截斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有辦法找他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子已經解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名偵探毛利小五郎不是浪得虛名吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.38,0:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什麼職業殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是讓警方一直束手無策的殺手FOX嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.23,0:11:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼他會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來了 潮先生到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經抓到FOX 他現在露臉也沒有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 那個老先生也不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個到底出了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會已經把他們兩個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我根本不是什麼FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在再裝蒜也沒有用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你還是老老實實的從實招來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利叔叔 你看這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河邊先生的包包裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多錢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血 上面也有血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.12,0:12:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.53,0:12:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個跟恭子姐姐包包裡那些一萬元鈔票上面的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.55,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 你快來聽一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.11,0:12:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名遭到殺害的田中先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查發現原本是一個暴力集團的主要份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.23,0:12:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方推測他們與此暴力集團之間存在某種爭執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這兩名男女嫌疑犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在威脅了被害人田中先生將金庫打開之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其中大約一億元的現金搶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據分析這是一宗強盜殺人案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩名男女嫌疑犯就是河邊先生和恭子小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個被害人所屬的暴力組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許派出人在到處追他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他們才會那麼的慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這些鈔票上面的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個被害人的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.88,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個傢伙今天早上又把共犯恭子小姐給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子的確是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我認為你們是來追我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他一定以為叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.09,0:13:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個被害者所屬的暴力組織雇來抓他們兩個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.41,0:13:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才亂了手腳和恭子小姐起了內訌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想殺我的也是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.88,0:13:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒辦法了 我看我們去自首好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳別傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙我會把他解決掉的 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要再殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果這麼做的話 我就去報警了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不應該跟妳生氣的 恭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不殺了她的話 我自己也會有危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.21,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 早知道我就不應該逃到這個山上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.54,0:14:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有殺那個大學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有跟那個什麼FOX的殺手也沒有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX到底會是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是現在最大的關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX絕對不可能錯過這次這麼好的一個機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 傳真(fax)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該有傳真機吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.90,0:14:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.10,0:14:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就是跟登山辦公室聯絡的傳真機啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個和公用電話用的應該是不同的線路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是它沒有被那陣雷切斷的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就可以聯絡警方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們真的只有下山去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話線被人切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.49,0:15:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為電話線是因為雷擊的關係被切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是在休息站裡被切斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話線是被人切斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.97,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.08,0:15:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是健一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要過去打擾你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.61,0:15:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.83,0:15:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面一定有線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.18,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井哥哥真的是定期到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.85,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在大學裡參加的是登山社 這很自然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這就是平井健一被殺害理由的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.87,0:15:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.22,0:15:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找潮先生的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有通知警方這兩件事得分開來進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我就留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大家監視這個傢伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.21,0:16:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下必須請你跟我一起行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.49,0:16:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼到現在還在懷疑我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想把皮膚給曬黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其今天才下過一陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽一定會曬得特別厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人才會怕曬太陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到山上爬山會曬到太陽 這是當然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曬太陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我終於明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於知道是哪裡不對勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.07,0:16:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老先生既然是這裡的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚不可能還是那麼的白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.35,0:16:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本就是別人假裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.69,0:16:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說那個老先生不是這裡的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道這種事情的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果是這裡的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會常常受到紫外線的照射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那皮膚應該會曬黑才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.51,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得那個老先生的皮膚白了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.85,0:16:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來那個老先生就是FOX嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那平井先生就是他殺的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平井先生本來就認識這裡的那個管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井先生如果到了休息站的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.66,0:17:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那FOX冒充管理員的事情就會被揭穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以FOX才會先把平井哥哥殺掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們在辦入山手續那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井先生在打電話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.42,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他就在路上就把平井先生殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後事先繞到休息站把電話線切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.29,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣他就可以等待他的獵物上門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.89,0:17:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後他就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒充起比登山客都還要熟悉山況的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.23,0:17:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要親手抓到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在已經知道FOX是什麼人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.69,0:17:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻不知道他在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.69,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是FOX嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.43,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX是職業殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.49,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會找出比任何人都還要快速脫逃的路徑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會選擇一條最近的下山路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.16,0:18:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.90,0:18:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.96,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是潮先生的錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片是他女兒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木幼稚園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得她是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.82,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定沒有想到自己要攻擊的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會對你進行反擊吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他這是在為他最愛的女兒報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.13,0:18:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.34,0:18:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經殺過一個高利貸公司的社長對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時他的車子不巧撞上了一輛幼稚園巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個學生就這樣死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚園巴士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別說你不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.08,0:18:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我唯一的女兒千里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是被你害死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.11,0:19:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是潮先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於FOX的長相、來歷、背景完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無計可施之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會以他自己的性命為誘餌把你引出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.85,0:19:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會去拜託毛利叔叔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那次的槍擊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.24,0:19:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是我拜託一個朋友幫忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.31,0:19:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是要讓毛利先生上鉤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.90,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為FOX是那個姓河邊的小夥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有想到這個老頭當了人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把他給推下去逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候誰是真正的職業殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就一目了然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.33,0:19:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小傷算不了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的千里受到的傷害要比這個大得多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿命來吧 FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.68,0:20:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你嘗盡了痛苦 痛苦的死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.57,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.78,0:20:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算這麼做了 千里她也不會再回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果殺了他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叔叔你自己也變成一個殺人兇手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為千里看到你這樣 她會快樂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.79,0:20:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死到臨頭還不悔悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是FOX沒錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 管理員先生就是FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.70,0:21:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 我毛利小五郎的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.69,0:21:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.92,0:21:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.73,0:21:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOX是年紀這麼輕的小夥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.59,0:22:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實真正的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.54,0:22:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被FOX關在休息站附近一個石穴裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.80,0:22:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著警方也終於趕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.16,0:22:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業殺手FOX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.41,0:22:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和強盜殺人兇手河邊晃就這樣被逮捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.88,0:22:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於潮先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.70,0:23:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 你還真不是泛泛之輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.73,0:23:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.02,0:23:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.36,0:23:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是把案子給解決掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.64,0:23:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家以後我要好好洗個熱水澡 然後吃個火鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.91,0:23:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這位叔叔也不是泛泛之輩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.23,0:23:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了 可以吃火鍋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.37,0:23:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.13,0:23:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.02,0:23:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.14,0:23:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像總是戴著眼鏡耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.03,0:24:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是睡覺還是洗澡的時候都戴著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.27,0:24:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.16,0:24:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不戴的話會很不安的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,407)}{\frz19}和新一拍攝於魔術表演時…
